PRIVACY POLICY
Hong Kong NetEase Interactive Entertainment Limited
(
"NetEase"
,
"we"
or
"us"
) wants you to be familiar with how we collect, use and disclose Personal Information.  If you are a resident of the European Economic Area (
"EEA"
), United Kingdom, or any other jurisdictions with applicable data protection laws, NetEase is the controller of your personal data.
"Personal Information"
is information that identifies you as an individual or relates to an identifiable individual. This Privacy Policy describes our processing practices of
Personal Information
that we collect and use in connection with:
•	Websites operated by us from which you are accessing this Privacy Policy (the
"Websites"
);
•	Gaming and software applications made available by us for use on or through computers, consoles and mobile devices (the
"Apps"
);
•	Our social media pages from which you are accessing this Privacy Policy (collectively, our
"Social Media Pages"
), such as our official fan pages on
Twitter
,
YouTube
, and
Facebook
and fan pages for our individual Apps;
•	Email messages that we send to you that link to this Privacy Policy or other communications with you; and
•	Offline business interactions you have with us.
Collectively, we refer to the Websites, Apps, Social Media Pages, emails, and offline business interactions as the
"Services"
.
