Connecting Your Services to Social Media
When you connect your Services account to your gaming and/or social media account (e.g., NetEase Games Account, Apple, Discord, Facebook, Google, LINE or Twitter) you will share information with your friends associated with your gaming and/or social media account, with other users, and with your gaming and/or social media account provider. By doing so, you authorize us to facilitate this sharing of information, and you understand that the use of shared information will be governed by the gaming and/or social media account provider's Privacy Policy.
For this sharing of account information, we are jointly responsible with the provider of the third-party gaming and/or social media account. We are, however, not responsible for any other collection or use of your Personal Information by these providers. Depending on the gaming and/or social media account that you choose to connect to your Services account, this means that we are jointly responsible with the following parties for the sharing of your Personal Information:
•
Apple
, which collects and uses your Personal Information in accordance with the
Apple Privacy Policy
;
•
Discord
, which collects and uses your Personal Information in accordance with the
Discord Privacy Policy
;
•
Epic Games
, which collects and uses your Personal Information in accordance with the
Epic Games Privacy Policy
;
•
Exptional Pte. Ltd.
, which collects and uses your Personal Information in accordance with the
NetEase Games Account Privacy Policy
;
•
Facebook
, which collects and uses your Personal Information in accordance with the
Meta Privacy Policy
;
•
Google
, which collects and uses your Personal Information in accordance with the
Google Privacy Policy
;
•
LINE
, which collects and uses your Personal Information in accordance with the
LINE Privacy Policy
;
•
Microsoft
, which collects and uses your Personal Information in accordance with the
Microsoft Privacy Statement
;
•
Sony
, which collects and uses your Personal Information in accordance with the
PlayStation Privacy Policy
;
•
